data.description: PRICE REDUCED!  FRESHLY PAINTED inside and out.  Ready to spend hours outdoors dipping in the pool or listening to the waterfall or watching golfers as they make their way down the golf course? This house has the perfect backyard if this is what you have dreamed off.  Come and put your own stamp on this beautiful Ibis II model home. This home comes with a new roof, updated kitchen, skeeter beater and new pool cage scheduled to be put on in February. The entire home has been setup with reverse Osmosis water system. Did we mentiond the golf cart is also included. Herons Glen boasts a brand new championship 18 hole golf course, 6 Har-Tru lighted tennis courts, 6 pickleball courts, brand new state-of-the-art fitness center, bocce, shuffleboard, resort style pool/spa, and a fabulous bar and restaurant! Call for your private tour today!
